abstract: At least 35 people are killed in two separate bombings in Nigeria.
lead_paragraph: Bombings in the north-central city of Jos and the northeastern town of Biu on Thursday left at least 35 people dead, officials said.

headline.main: Nigeria: Blasts Kill at Least 35 People
